<%- include('../layouts/header') %>
<div class="container mt-5">
   <div class="row justify-content-center g-4">
      <div class="col-lg-5">
         <div class="card shadow-lg p-4 border-0 rounded-4 h-100">
            <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">Thong tin don hang</h4>
            <p class="mb-2"><strong>Phim:</strong> <%= booking.showtimeId.movieId.title %></p>
            <p class="mb-2"><strong>Rap:</strong> <%= booking.showtimeId.cinemaId.name %> - <%= booking.showtimeId.roomId.name %></p>
            <p class="mb-2"><strong>Ghe:</strong> <%= booking.tickets.map(t => t.code).join(', ') %></p>
            <p class="mb-2"><strong>Tam tinh:</strong> <%= (booking.subtotalAmount || booking.totalAmount).toLocaleString('vi-VN') %>d</p>
            <p class="mb-2"><strong>Giam gia:</strong> -<%= (booking.discountAmount || 0).toLocaleString('vi-VN') %>d
              <% if (booking.discountCode) { %>
                <span class="badge bg-warning text-dark ms-2"><%= booking.discountCode %></span>
              <% } %>
            </p>
            <hr>
            <h5 class="text-danger fw-bold">Tong thanh toan: <%= booking.totalAmount.toLocaleString('vi-VN') %>d</h5>
            <p class="text-secondary small mb-0">Sau khi xac nhan, he thong se sinh ve dien tu de in hoac luu PDF.</p>
         </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-lg-5">
         <div class="card shadow-lg p-4 border-0 rounded-4 text-center h-100">
            <h4 class="text-danger mb-3"><i class="bi bi-qr-code-scan"></i> Thanh toan QR</h4>
            <div class="mb-3">
               <img src="<%= qrUrl %>" alt="QR Code Payment" class="img-fluid border rounded" style="max-width: 300px;">
            </div>
            <p class="text-secondary small">Mo ung dung ngan hang va quet ma de thanh toan. Day la luong demo, xac nhan sau khi chuyen khoan.</p>
            <p class="bg-dark p-2 rounded small text-start">
               <strong>Noi dung CK:</strong> Thanh toan ve <%= booking._id.toString().substring(18) %>
            </p>

            <form action="/bookings/<%= booking._id %>/confirm" method="POST" class="mt-3">
               <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success btn-lg px-5 rounded-pill shadow">Da thanh toan - Tao ve dien tu</button>
            </form>
            <div class="mt-3">
               <a href="/bookings/history" class="text-muted">Quay lai lich su dat ve</a>
            </div>
         </div>
      </div>
   </div>
</div>
<%- include('../layouts/footer') %>
